lyrics:
[Verse]
In the cyberpunk future, a world unknown
Where everyone's high on life, problems disowned
Bright neon lights, illuminating our dreams
No worries, no fears, just bliss it seems

[Chorus]
Living in a utopia, where everything's fine
No troubles, no pain, just a dream divine
Dancing in the streets, with joy in our souls
In this cyberpunk future, we've reached our goals
